value.description:
- Value can be an Integer eg `100` ( if type is any of the following: `cart-price` or `cart-weight` ).
- Value can be an String eg `"Dress"` or `"VIP"` ( if type is any of the following: `category` or `customer-group` ).
- Value can also be an array of objects containing `lng` and `lat` (if type is specific-area ) eg [
        `{
          "lat": 14.919427692528,
          "lng": 36.7360729
        }
      ]`
